post_text: Does anyone out there have information they could share?
shared_text:
Neal Alan Cruse
June 16, 2017 at 3:28 PM ¬∑

Oswego is celebrating 150 years of sports. We need information on any athlete/coach that went to Oswego from 1967 to the present. Those sports include girls and boys basketball, football, volleyball, cross-country/track, baseball (little league, babe ruth, high school), Softball (little league etc.), fast pitch softball, bowling and golf. Information we need:

* Coached state teams or went to state as an athlete
* Was selected to an All State Team

If you have any information that would be helpful please let us know. We would like to have this information by June 23 if possible. Please provide documentation for the information you provide. Thank you for any help you can provide.
